    "description": "Discipline: Qinggong\nSkill: Athletics TN 6\nType: Normal\nQi: 3\n\nYou move effortlessly, bending your body to find every shadow and unseen space to elude the vision of foes. You also lighten your body, making your steps soundless. On a success you can are incredibly difficult to spot. This means anyone making a Detect roll against your Stealth to spot you, must make two consecutive Detect rolls to succeed. You need to roll this anytime someone might see you. If you do anything to call attention to your presence, the Technique will not work (for example stabbing someone in the face). Cathartic: When used Cathartically the effect lasts for ten minutes.",
